HEADWORD: Bidale
<hw>Bid"ale`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Bid</ets> +
<ets>ale</ets>.]</ety> <def>An invitation of friends to drink ale at
some poor man's house, and there to contribute in charity for his
relief.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

